Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:24.30,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the skies that are still unknown to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:28.40,Default,op,0,0,0,,I know, you're doing just the same -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.98,Default,op,0,0,0,,Dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.24,Default,op,0,0,0,,Just a small glow\NFrom those great days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:38.12,Default,op,0,0,0,,Is what dragging you along
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:41.87,Default,op,0,0,0,,Giving you faith and some comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:45.79,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the sun that scorches badly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:52.17,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only want to see your guise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.91,Default,op,0,0,0,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.18,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only watch \NWith tears on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:04.77,Default,op,0,0,0,,As you slowly disappear in this noon haze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.76,Default,op,0,0,0,,We're alone \NWe're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.31,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Walking this world on our own
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.36,0:01:16.53,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}Looking for each other since long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:22.49,Default,op,0,0,0,,In the end, in the end, \NAfter the day we finally meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:27.00,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord1\blur1\t(2100,2200,\shad3\blur3\c&HABADD8&)}We won't ever have to say "Goodbye"
Comment: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP END}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The New York - Boston express bus \Nis carrying me through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Maki, for the moment, I am heading to Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I'll see Todo taking part in preliminaries \Nfor getting into the US Pro Circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's one more person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrained by Todo's burning enthusiasm,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa Ranko now follows us \Nto become a preliminaries challenger as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We should arrive to Boston tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Todo and Midorikawa, \Nalong with the rest of the passengers, are having a sound sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,On this nocturnal highway,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe, no one else except bus driver and me \Nis staring into that darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, \NI can't sleep at all, Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo and Midorikawa embarked this bus \Nbecause they have own, clearly defined goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Comparing myself to them, I can't help asking, \Nwhat on Earth am I going to Boston for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Those thoughts deprive me of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I could finally meet Todo, as I so craved to. \NAnd I should, by all means, be happy to be riding the same bus now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Maki. Maki?\NI'm not doing something wrong, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not making a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:53.00,Default,,0,0,100,,{\an8\bord4\blur15\3c&HAC907F&\t(0,1000,\bord0\blur1)\c&HFEFEFD&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\3a&H2D&\fscx184\fscy156}Episode 7
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,120,,{\b0\fs30\blur1\fnVerdana\bord0.8\c&HE1E4E4&\1a&H11&}Boston
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo just threw his luggage into the room \Nand went out for a roadwork at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He is really fired about about that fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what a morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa, do you mind if I have a little nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. It's just me who has to wake up early. \NThe preliminaries are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go find us a permanent court for practices. \NSign the contract and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's time for breakfast, \NI'll wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you couldn't sleep in that cramped bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I take your word for it \Nand have just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to give this one to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't bring along a racket, did you? \NI'm giving you my spare one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I need an opponent. Won't you refuse me a match\Nfor the first time in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't see that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But I just so much \Nwanted to see you, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How most unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One could never tell you turned southpaw just recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. When I was playing with my right, \Nthe power was times more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not true! Your serve, your forehand \Nand your ball drive are no inferior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of tending to me, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a single clue regarding what kind of stuff \Nis going on in Japan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But shouldn't autumn tennis season be in full swing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of making the best of your youth, \Nyou are wasting your time training here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think something's just a bit off here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I don't expect you to answer. \NEveryone has their own different reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has the right \Nto do whatever they please and how they want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not for me to accuse others of being self-indulgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But this one time \Nit seems you're really under quite a pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much pain you experience along the way, \Nyou should never use it as an excuse to give yourself an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Should never use it to hamper others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, you should give this advantage to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have always adhered to that tenet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Give advantage to a partner and wait patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Although eventually my partner left for elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Advantage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Oka! \NThat's a great ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At such moments...\NAt moments like this, I wish the time would stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hotel is about 5 kilo away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't we conclude the training \Nwith a scenic Tour de Boston?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. \NLet's ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The first to arrive gets $1. \NBut the other two pay for the winner's dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just get a dessert with coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a positive okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! That was a head start! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the three of us, Maki. \NStill I'm so exceedingly happy, Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow it feels that after that, \NI will never forget the wonderful moments of today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A bicycle ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A man I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A city in the dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just forget about everything \Nand YELL my lungs out in delight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad Maki. \NI am so glad to have finally seen Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Maki. Truly so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! That's it, Oka. \NYou should also apply!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For preliminaries. You and me still have enough time \Nto make entry in doubles together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Together we can put the local yellow pros to flight! \NWell? Isn't it a fine idea? Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We both happened to be in America. \NIsn't it a great chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But think again. I was not planning to stay here for long. \NI have a lot of loose ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the issue? Money? A hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'll gladly sort it out for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down a bit there, player Midorikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka's full-time hot-tempered Coach Mr. Katsura, \Nis waiting for her back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, such matters \Nare not to be decided solely on Oka's volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call him! Trust me. \NWe'll reach a compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no worries! If Munakata's sister is in charge, \Neven his heart will bend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind I know Daigo ever since I was in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus the stuff Jin told about him, \Nhe's like the back of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't feel like I drank that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However fine your idea is,\Nit can't be incarnated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Oka takes part in this tournament, \Nher amateur qualification is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After returning to Japan, \NOka could no longer play in amateur events.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's not about Mr. Katsura only. \NMadame Butterfly is also likely to be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tennis will be tennis. Pro or amateur - \Nno diffeence, whassoewhaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa, are you feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say nonsenth. Chattering like this with you two \Nwill not tire me one bit in eternithee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If ye excuse me, \NI'll be heading to the room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Goodnight! \N- Good... night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sincerely happy \Nthat I was able to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, until yesterday \NI felt like I'm on the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I got myself together \Nand will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me, how is it going for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been doing fine, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have been doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a hitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's all I need to know then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning! Are you awake? It's Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in, it's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Big news, big news!\NWait... Where's Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a morning shower. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm not sure how to put it, \Nbut Mr. Sayama called me from New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This evening our friend Chiba \Nis to arrive to Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Questionable things I don't want Todo to know \Nhappened back in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Oka!\NWe're here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a little cold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing fine, Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But first, how come? \NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... This and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when Mr. Sayama reported meeting Midorikawa, \NI was utterly amazed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only reborn as a southpaw \Nbut also determined to transfer to pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have always been an impulsive shopper. \NIt was Todo who became a catalyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I never gave it much of a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, you should not get up just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she just has a little fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain caught us by surprise during practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,First thing in the morning we'll go to the hospital. \NShe is burning like a bonfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dismal to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if you excuse us, we'll head back to the room. \NSee you tomorrow, Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, don't exert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tokyo Cup was \Ngracefully won by Madame Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Reckon she's working as hard as always. \NWell, how is Oka doing then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She didn't want to talk \Nabout anything related to the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Although she seems to be most troublefree every single day, \Nto tell you the truth, I'm kinda worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears, Oka had to go through impossible to get here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If Oka decided not to tell you, \Nthen I shouldn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I believe, she's doing it for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It all started because you never reported back to us \Nthat you lost your first match here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not about Oka alone. For me, Ozaki and Madame Butterfly \Nit caused unnecessary worries as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to accept responsibility for making Oka worried \Nbuy living through this anxiety yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:16:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka was eliminated from Tokyo Cup by a rookie in the first round.\NMoreover, she refused the repechage match in order to go see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However difficult it was before, \Nshe never gave up a match before even trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to blame everything on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But this turned into nothing but minuses for both of you. \NIt's just deplorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's deplorable, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki, I spent the next three days \Nrecovering motionless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, on the day of Todo's match, \NI could finally go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,First round, first set. \NTakayuki Todo versus Ed Kartrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Service play - Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:17:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no other chance to talk to Todo, \Nas I spent the last few days sleeping mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But on that day, Todo's determination to win this match \Nwas in the air, as if he was channeling it to audience somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was almost as if I was playing this match myself. \NAs if I was swinging the racket myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the first time I experienced such a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,15-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,30-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,40-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to his New York matches, \Nhe looks more spirited now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Todo finally decided to live up \Nto his Japan Open champion title.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the opponent is also a player, \Nwho won the East Coast Amateur Championship twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,40-15!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Their abilities are about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory and defeat are equally probable in this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Todo is good at handling the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter if he wins or loses, \Nwe won't see him weeping over his helplessness from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Deuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Deuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Deuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Advantage: Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This was your first victory in America. \NAccept my congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In the second round, in the third round, and of course, \Neven in the final round, keep doing your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I think, tomorrow\NI'm coming back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:20:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I know I came to America without warning. \NAnd I'm sure, I caused a lot of nuisance for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,However, having that said, \NI still have one more request.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you win or lose, \Ntell me about it in letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Especially{\i0} when you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This way I can have no worries \Neven when you're away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured we should celebrate \NTodo's first victory in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And if Midorikawa performs just as great \Nin women matches tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,how many more champagnes will I drink while here? \NYou can never tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect much on my side.\NIt's still more of a try-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Todo said the other day, \Nyour southpaw ball is even sharper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He really did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we wait a little longer? \NFor those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, even if for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one here who should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who hampered you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after I said that I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You regret saying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That's not the way for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this time, \Nlet me take this little advantage of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Advantage, Oka.
Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:22.52,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:28.15,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:31.11,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings mixed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:33.99,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:39.18,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:46.09,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:51.47,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:58.35,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:04.77,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:13.96,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.96,0:23:19.16,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:22.21,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:25.25,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:30.78,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa Maki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, finally, you're back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks for beautiful souvenirs for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But upon returning, you're engaged again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The tough university coach takes you under his authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Coach Katsura wasn't always that harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still must fight, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Queen's Cup is coming, and you should be triumphal on it! \NTriumphal! Right, Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "The Final Repechage Match."
